      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve 1/2&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span>&nbsp;<strong>chicken</strong>&nbsp;<strong>stock cube</strong>&nbsp;in a heatproof bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]&nbsp;</span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong>, cover, and set aside until serving</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>honey</strong> and remaining <strong>chicken</strong>&nbsp;<strong>stock cube</strong> in 350ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [700ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; this is your <strong>honey&nbsp;stock</strong></p>",
